      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"{\\\"issues\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":4808837573,\\\"number\\\":15,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Swift Playgrounds in the notebook programming section?\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Can [Swift Playgrounds](https://developer.apple.com/swift-playgrounds/) be mentioned as an example of an interactive and exploratory programming environment in the notebook programming section of the potpourri page? I think macOS (and iPadOS) users might find this interesting and useful.\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"comments\\\":0,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:01Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:01Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808837442,\\\"number\\\":14,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Safari in Q\\\\u0026A\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"I think that the [last part of the Q\\\\u0026A](https://github.com/missing-semester/missing-semester/blob/master/_2020/qa.md#any-comments-on-differences-between-web-browsers) undersells the merits of Safari. Firefox excels for privacy reasons as you mention, but so does Safari. The lower memory footprint and battery life usage are benefits of Safari that aren't mentioned.\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"comments\\\":4,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:58Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:01Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4808836351,\\\"number\\\":9,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Add common network/DNS tools to debugging?\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Thanks for the great content in this series.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nIn the \\\\\\\"Debugging\\\\\\\" lecture, it would be useful to add `netcat` or `telnet` to the list of tools to use when debugging network issues. As well, listing `dig` or `nslookup` and `host` or `getent hosts` would be helpful in cases of debugging DNS issues. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nA couple of examples where these are used from my experiences as a software engineer:\\\\r\\\\n* working through issues with firewalls in public cloud or on premise\\\\r\\\\n* debugging VPN setup issues\\\\r\\\\n\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"comments\\\":3,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:43Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:45Z\\\"}],\\\"pageInfo\\\":{\\\"endCursor\\\":\\\"Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyNi0wNy0wNFQxMTo0Nzo0M1rPAAAAAR6hBP8=\\\",\\\"hasNextPage\\\":false,\\\"hasPreviousPage\\\":false,\\\"startCursor\\\":\\\"Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyNi0wNy0wNFQxMTo0ODowMVrPAAAAAR6hCcU=\\\"},\\\"totalCount\\\":3}\", \"annotations\": null, \"meta\": null}], \"structuredContent\": null, \"isError\": false}"
