.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nSSH is very unintuitive, so the explanation of keys, \\\\u0026 port-forwarding is extremely valuable. I've added here a section on how to do \\\\\\\"SSH Proxying\\\\\\\" because that's another common use case. From their perspective \\\\\\\"my data is on host B behind SSH server A, and I want to download (upload) it\\\\\\\" is extremely common.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nHopefully this repo/class is still being loved and can be updated!\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n_This PR was originally from a fork: **nyetsche/missing-semester** (branch: `ssh-proxy`)_\\\",\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:13Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:13Z\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"draft\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/pulls/21\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"http