    "result": {
      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"[{\\\"id\\\":4881863060,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"IC_kwDOTNbyO88AAAABIvtRlA\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"*Original author: @jonhoo_r5pp*\\\\n\\\\nMy personal take on this is that these days there is very little reason to use Safari over Chrome or Firefox. @JJGO_hh3b @anishathalye_hs2x ?\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"reactions\\\":{\\\"total_count\\\":0,\\\"+1\\\":0,\\\"-1\\\":0,\\\"laugh\\\":0,\\\"confused\\\":0,\\\"heart\\\":0,\\\"hooray\\\":0,\\\"rocket\\\":0,\\\"eyes\\\":0,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881863060/reactions\\\"},\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:59Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:59Z\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881863060\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/14#issuecomment-4881863060\\\",\\\"issue_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/14\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4881863106,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"IC_kwDOTNbyO88AAAABIvtRwg\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"*Original author: @JJGO_3ozd*\\\\n\\\\nIt's not so clear-cut for me. On macOS Chrome eats up ridiculous amounts of RAM whereas Safari is noticeably more efficient. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nRegarding privacy, both support uBlock Origin which does most of the heavy lifting and both lack neater features like Multi-Account Containers. Chrome also has a track record of not respecting privacy when it comes to Google sites [source](https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=24817304).\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nI also like Safari's compatibility. Whenever a website is giving me trouble because of my browser setup in Firefox, I'll use Safari and it works 100% of time.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nTL;DR: If I had to stop using Firefox, I'll probably use Safari as my default\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"reactions\\\":{\\\"total_count\\\":0,\\\"+1\\\":0,\\\"-1\\\":0,\\\"laugh\\\":0,\\\"confused\\\":0,\\\"heart\\\":0,\\\"hooray\\\":0,\\\"rocket\\\":0,\\\"eyes\\\":0,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881863106/reactions\\\"},\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:00Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:00Z\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881863106\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/14#issuecomment-4881863106\\\",\\\"issue_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/14\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4881863146,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"IC_kwDOTNbyO88AAAABIvtR6g\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"*Original author: @anishathalye_wzc3*\\\\n\\\\nWe currently say:\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\u003e Should you want an alternative, Firefox is our recommendation.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nShould we switch to clearly stating that Firefox is our recommended browser, and de-emphasize Chrome / mention any privacy problems with it? I personally use Firefox, Jose does too, and iirc Jon does as well?\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nIt might also be worth mentioning Chromium, the slightly de-Google'd version of Chrome (though it's missing things like automatic updates). I currently use Chromium on the rare occasion where a site that I need to use does not work properly in Firefox.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nAlso, like @AustinConlon_7xsh suggested, maybe we could say a bit more about Safari being a privacy-respecting browser. (I don't know as much about the memory/battery story of Safari vs Firefox currently, but if there's data on this, we can mention/link it too).\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"reactions\\\":{\\\"total_count\\\":0,\\\"+1\\\":0,\\\"-1\\\":0,\\\"laugh\\\":0,\\\"confused\\\":0,\\\"heart\\\":0,\\\"hooray\\\":0,\\\"rocket\\\":0,\\\"eyes\\\":0,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881863146/reactions\\\"},\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:00Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:48:00Z\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881863146\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/14#issuecomment-4881863146\\\",\\\"issue_url\\\":\\\"https: