s_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"reactions\\\":{\\\"total_count\\\":0,\\\"+1\\\":0,\\\"-1\\\":0,\\\"laugh\\\":0,\\\"confused\\\":0,\\\"heart\\\":0,\\\"hooray\\\":0,\\\"rocket\\\":0,\\\"eyes\\\":0,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881862316/reactions\\\"},\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:44Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T11:47:44Z\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/comments/4881862316\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/9#issuecomment-4881862316\\\",\\\"issue_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/issues/9\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4881862345,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"IC_kwDOTNbyO88AAAABIvtOyQ\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"*Original author: @flindeberg_ic24*\\\\n\\\\nSome more potentially interesting topics in the realm of networking:\\\\r\\\\n- `dns` as in the protocol and actual implementation\\\\r\\\\n- `delv`, i.e. a `dig`-like tool with some DNSSEC-magic\\\\r\\\\n- Captive portals, (CG)NAT and similar solutions\\\\r\\\\n- `.local` domain, `mDNS`, `zeroconf` and the interaction with Chromecasts, AppleTV, etc\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"